{"tid":719210,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 蘭仙尼收咧","createTime":"2018-06-27T08:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T09:06:47.000Z","uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9012b0065e8765b208c07477c39234b2d81c2085","tid":719210,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:56:35.000Z","msg":"阿根廷國腳蘭仙尼禍不單行，因傷無緣世界盃之餘，最新消息指他在新球季難望復出。<br />\n今年25歲的蘭仙尼（Manuel Lanzini）備戰世界盃期間受傷，膝傷情況嚴重，最新消息指將要倦勤15個月之久，意味著新球季不可能重返球場，提早收爐。消息更指，蘭仙尼膝部韌帶撕裂，情況遠比想像中嚴重，就算養傷期縮短至1年，基本上也不可能在季尾前回復比賽狀態。 韋斯咸新球季將由新帥柏歷堅尼接手，至今先後簽下3名新援，即使蘭仙尼是近3季主力，復出後能否取回正選也是未知數。 上季英超，這位阿根廷翼鋒上陣27場射入5球，近3季各項賽事總上陣99場，射入20球。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%85%98-%E8%98%AD%E4%BB%99%E5%B0%BC%E9%87%8D%E5%82%B7%E6%95%B4%E5%AD%A3%E9%9B%A3%E5%BE%A9%E5%87%BA-080037581--spt.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2585%2598-%25E8%2598%25AD%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2582%25B7%25E6%2595%25B4%25E5%25AD%25A3%25E9%259B%25A3%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E5%2587%25BA-080037581--spt.html&d=mQW3N00r1XXfZyNZcpRAQBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=676a0838\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%85%98-%E8%98%AD%E4%BB%99%E5%B0%BC%E9%87%8D%E5%82%B7%E6%95%B4%E5%AD%A3%E9%9B%A3%E5%BE%A9%E5%87%BA-080037581--spt.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www1.pictures.zimbio.com/gi/Nicolas+Otamendi+Manuel+Lanzini+Manchester+xUk_lX56xMbl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww1.pictures.zimbio.com%2Fgi%2FNicolas%2BOtamendi%2BManuel%2BLanzini%2BManchester%2BxUk_lX56xMbl.jpg&h=fd6edbd2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2829719c14a21d8e6f902fd93b409030ceca2cb","tid":719210,"uid":102096,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:57:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d77fd53051dd48303ac08ed98b8d84d181f22b6","tid":719210,"uid":5649,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:58:30.000Z","msg":"一年得24個月，佢傷左15個月<br />\n即係唔洗踢架啦啵<img src